(2, 36, 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy-policy', '', '<p><strong>Disclaimer</strong></p>\r\n<p>OrganizationName is committed to your privacy. <br /> Although most information on this site is accessible without having to provide personal data, you may occasionally be requested to provide personal information. By providing this information you explicitly allow OrganizationName to store your personal data for the purpose of automated user profiling, customer management, market research and direct mailing services. In this case, the data will be processed in accordance with the provisions and requirements of Directive 2009/136/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 25 November 2009 concerning the processing of personal data. Your personal data will only be used for purposes strictly related to OrganizationNameâ€™s services and will not be communicated to third parties. <br /> You may always oppose to the use of your personal data for direct marketing purposes by contacting OrganizationName. You also have the right to access, update or correct your personal data at any time by accessing the appropriate system, where available, or by contacting OrganizationName. You can contact OrganizationName by email: name at organizationname dot TLD or post: OrganizationName address.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Automatically obtained non-personal data</strong></p>\r\n<p>OrganizationName may anonymously gather non-personal data such as your browser type or IP-address, operating system used, or the domain name of the website through which you reached or left on the Websites.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cookies</strong></p>\r\n<p>When accessing the Websites, cookies (small text files) can be placed on your computerâ€™s hard drive to provide you with a more personalised website experience. The configuration of most Internet browsers allows you to accept or reject cookies, and to be alerted before a cookie is installed. Rejecting the use of cookies can impact the navigability of the Websites. Acceptin